game.name: Sara’s Rhubarb Pie
game.description:
One of the most popular free online cooking games among girls of all ages, Sara Rhubarb Pie game features high-quality graphics and easy control to gaming enthusiasts. Rhubarb pie ? a little sour and a little sweet ? makes sure that your taste buds will surely enjoy and will remember the taste of this delicious dish for a long time. In this electrifying and exciting cooking game for girls, your goal is to help Sara to bake the most scrumptious rhubarb pie.  

Since Sara is the best chef in the world and also very helping in nature so you would also get a chance to learn a lot from her. In Sara cooking class, your knowledge about various cooking ingredients will encourage you to propel in the right direction and deliver the best for her. Roll up your sleeves to prepare a rhubarb pie in the optimum possible manner. Do not ignore the Sara instructions to bake this mouth-watering dessert perfectly. In order to earn the bonus points, try to bake it at the least possible time.   

When you play this cool flash game in your browser, you will surely have a chance to learn how to bake extremely delicious pie quickly and perfectly. All you need to do is mix all the useful ingredients and get it prepared to satisfy your craving for pie. Start making the filling once the dough is prepared and then put in the oven. Be attentive while keeping your eyes on its time tracking and get ready to serve it in front of her.
